Monet in the '90s - The Series Paintings
Museum of Fine Arts | 1989 | ISBN: 0300046596 | English | 332 pages | PDF | 60.3 MB

The Museum of Fine Arts is honored that Digital Equipment Corporation has chosen to sponsor the exhibition and catalogue Monet in the '90s: The Series Paintings. This unprecedented exhibition presents 90 series paintings created by the great Impressionist master in the 1890s
